globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Pytest exclusively for Python backend testing without alternatives
- Use Vitest exclusively for frontend unit testing without alternatives
- Use Playwright exclusively for end-to-end testing without alternatives
- Run complete test suites before marking any development task complete
- Fix all failing tests before proceeding to next development phase
- Generate test reports in reports folder for analysis and debugging
- Maintain comprehensive test coverage for all implemented features